<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ - UPTM</title>
    <!-- Vapor Theme from Bootswatch -->
    <link href="https://bootswatch.com/5/vapor/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS for further styling -->
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .accordion-button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: 1px solid #0056b3;
        }

            .accordion-button:focus {
                box-shadow: none;
            }

        .accordion-item {
            border: 1px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .accordion-header {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #0056b3;
            border-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .accordion-body {
            background-color: #343a40; /* Dark background for the answers */
            color: white; /* White text for better contrast */
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
        }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

        .card-body ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

            .card-body ul li {
                list-style-type: disc;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container my-4">
        <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
            <!-- Question 1 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button btn btn-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        Q1: What are the categories of fees?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <ul>
                            <li>a. Tuition fees</li>
                            <li>b. Accommodation fees</li>
                            <li>c. Other fees</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h6>Payment Deadline</h6>
                        <ul>
                            <li>a. One month before final semester examination starts</li>
                            <li>b. Before end of the month</li>
                            <li>c. Before registration of new semester</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 2 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <button class="accordion-button btn btn-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        Q2: What is the method of payment?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Online payment through FPX - <a href="https://epay.kptm.edu.my" target="_blank" class="text-light">https://epay.kptm.edu.my</a> (please refer to Payment Manual).
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 3 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                    <button class="accordion-button btn btn-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Q3: I am eligible for sponsorship, do I have to pay the entire fee first?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        You just have to pay accommodation and other fees in full.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 4 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                    <button class="accordion-button btn btn-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                        Q4: I am not eligible for MARA sponsorship due to academic requirements. Do I have to pay all fees billed for Semester 1?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        Yes, you need to pay all semester 1 fees in full. You are encouraged to apply for PTPTN. For working parents, EPF withdrawal can be made to pay for tuition fees.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Question 5 -->
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                    <button class="accordion-button btn btn-dark" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                        Q5: Can I pay my tuition fees in instalments?
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        We MAY consider your partial payments. You need to complete all the documentation and obtain verification from your Mentor before the application can be approved by authorized officers.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS (bundle includes Popper) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
